# File and Folder Structure

## Root Directory

The root directory contains several important configuration files:

### Build and TypeScript Configuration
- [tsconfig.json](mdc:/tsconfig.json) - Base TypeScript configuration
- [vitest.config.ts](mdc:/vitest.config.ts) - Vitest test runner configuration
- [turbo.json](mdc:/turbo.json) - Turborepo pipeline configuration

### Code Quality
- [biome.jsonc](mdc:/biome.jsonc) - Biome formatter and linter config
- [.prettierrc.js](mdc:/.prettierrc.js) - Prettier formatting rules
- [.editorconfig](mdc:/.editorconfig) - Editor configuration
- [eslint.config.mjs](mdc:/eslint.config.mjs) - ESLint rules

### Package Management
- [pnpm-workspace.yaml](mdc:/pnpm-workspace.yaml) - Workspace definitions
- [package.json](mdc:/package.json) - Root package configuration
- [.npmrc](mdc:/.npmrc) - NPM configuration

## Main Directories

### Apps Directory (`apps/`)
Contains standalone applications:

```
apps/
└── storybook/           # Storybook documentation app
    ├── .storybook/     # Storybook configuration
    ├── stories/        # Story components
    └── package.json    # Storybook dependencies
```

### Packages Directory (`packages/`)
Contains shared libraries:

```
packages/
└── node-library/       # Node.js shared library
    ├── src/           # Source code
    ├── cjs/          # CommonJS build output
    ├── esm/          # ES Modules build output
    ├── tslib/        # TypeScript build output
    └── package.json  # Library dependencies
```

### Additional Directories
- `libraries/` - Additional shared libraries and components
- `tools/` - Development and build tooling
- `.changeset/` - Changesets for version management
- `.github/` - GitHub workflows and configuration
- `.husky/` - Git hooks for code quality
- `.vscode/` - VS Code editor settings

## Key Configuration Files

### Node Library Configuration
The `node-library` package uses multiple TypeScript configurations for different build targets:
- [packages/node-library/tsconfig.base.json](mdc:/packages/node-library/tsconfig.base.json) - Base configuration
- [packages/node-library/tsconfig.cjs.json](mdc:/packages/node-library/tsconfig.cjs.json) - CommonJS build
- [packages/node-library/tsconfig.esm.json](mdc:/packages/node-library/tsconfig.esm.json) - ES Modules build
- [packages/node-library/tsconfig.tslib.json](mdc:/packages/node-library/tsconfig.tslib.json) - TypeScript library build

